code: export function basis(t1,v0,v1,v2,v3){var t2=t1*t1,t3=t2*t1;return((1-3*t1+3*t2-t3)*v0+(4-6*t2+3*t3)*v1+(1+3*t1+3*t2-3*t3)*v2+t3*v3)/6;}export default function(values){var n=values.length-1;return function(t){var i=t<=0?t=0:t>=1?(t=1,n-1):Math.floor(t*n),v1=values[i],v2=values[i+1],v0=i>0?values[i-1]:2*v1-v2,v3=i<n-1?values[i+2]:2*v2-v1;return basis((t-i/n)*n,v0,v1,v2,v3);};}
